 Nightlight/Trinity::
Nightlight nodded and took in arms at Trinity who tried to free herself and ran out to face the inceticons "Let me go aunt Nightlight, Let me go out... I'll show them what a tiger sablethooh kitty can do...!!!"
  Rudra656@... wrote: ::Aerotaur:: 
      He lurches forward as the explosions quake through the mountain.  He sighs.  "I thought they had left."  He glances at the screen and waits for the second blast (the grenade) to shake the base.  He shakes his head and walks to the door.  He goes outside just far enough to get one shot off before he runs back inside.  He fires his one shot at the ground under the group, thus collapsing the ground under them a few feet due to the pit Terrataur had dug earlier.  He walks back inside to Nightlight.  "That should take them a little while to get out of.  We need to have a meeting.
